Release
-------

Install `twine <https://twine.readthedocs.io/en/stable/>`_.

.. code:: sh

    python setup.py sdist
    source .env # if you have stored TWINE_USERNAME and TWINE_PASSWORD
    twine upload dist/*
    
    
